[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那次难忘的约会之后，我和奈莉德之间多出了一种奇妙的默契。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也许是约会的余韵。谁也没有主动去找谁，偶然在基地遇见也是相视一笑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "谁也没有开口。每次见面，就能想到那个长长的吻，那种触感仿佛还停留在唇边。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "大概不会有人在接吻时开口，自然也不会主动打破这种久久都未消散的气氛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "于我而言，这样的奈莉德别有一番风情。至于我们的关系又如何变化，我暂时没有去想。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而当这种气氛还在持续的时候，奈莉德似乎要主动出击了——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我像往常一样结束了工作，回到房间里准备休息。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "忙吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "门没关，奈莉德倚在门框上，弯着嘴角。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不忙的话，一起去散散步？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她嘴角上扬的弧度好像藏着什么“阴谋诡计”——那就更有去看看的必要了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "天已经黑了。街道冷清，霓虹灯和月光映着倒影。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们肩并肩走着。手背有意无意地碰到，又自然而然地扣在一起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "走到那天睡着的公园，走过那家餐厅。晚风吹着头发，远处的招牌模糊，顺着街道铺向远方。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就这么沉默地走着。我感觉到她在酝酿着什么，要说些什么。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但猜不到，也不想打断她的思考。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就这么漫无目的地牵着手走着，直到灯也都熄灭了，只剩下凉凉夜色。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "基地大厅还亮着灯——不知道什么时候走到了这里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "走过走廊，走到她的房间里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有开灯，水族箱的灯成了唯一的光源。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她转过身，直视着我的眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我想了一路。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么开场。怎么收尾。怎么组织语言，怎么递进。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她顿了顿。我没有说话，等着她继续往下说。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "比调查报告难写多了。我好像确实不太擅长这个。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但是，该说的话还是要说的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她认真地看着我，深吸了一口气。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我爱你，playername。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我想说的就是这个，我爱你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "无论如何都想告诉你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不知道为什么，张口说这句话这么难。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但是我还是要说——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我爱你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有人比你更懂我。甚至比我自己更懂我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "和你在一起的每一分每一秒都恰到好处。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我一开始不理解。不明白这种感觉如何名状。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可能这就是幸福吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "谢谢你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "和你在一起，我很幸福。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "之所以要说这些——你可能有点莫名其妙——别急着摇头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为我感到遗憾。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我以前从不觉得需要什么仪式感。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不需要过生日。不需要过节日。不需要谁来陪我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可现在……我变了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "渴望和你在一起。度过更多时间，经历更多事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想要记住每一刻。哪怕是有点不知所谓的告白和有点简单笨拙的初吻。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哪怕是遗憾。我也想要记住。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "——我会陪在你身边的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "微笑着张开了双臂。怔了怔，她抱住了我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "阳光透过窗户洒在我的背上。尽管被我抱在怀里，但奈莉德已经走到了阳光下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不管发生什么。不管有多大的困难，我都会陪着你的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是我的回应，奈莉德。也是我的诺言。",
        "disable": 0
    }
]